        {
            "title": "中國去年新增人民幣貸款降至七年來最低 借款人需求疲軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中國去年新增人民幣貸款降至七年來最低 借款人需求疲軟\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3_alNLfygjssm64dqgUTEQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-05/5217bb60-18bc-11ef-99e7-32c46e8fbff6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國去年新增人民幣貸款降至七年來最低 借款人需求疲軟</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%83%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E-%E5%80%9F%E6%AC%BE%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F-082822447.html",
